Package com.BrethrenAce.GameEngine

Class Board.BoardBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.BrethrenAce.GameEngine.Board.BoardBuilder
Enclosing class:
Board
public static class Board.BoardBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
Class for building board configurations. This class sets and arranges the piece of each Tile of the Board. Required for Board initialization.
